name: KDA x CHEFSUTH 01
description: “Artist: Kellan David - This 1 of 1 digital artwork was released as a part of “the people’s art project” - an impact-focused art project series created by Kellan David, Aeterna Media and Minneapolis Haus of Design. All NFTs created as a part of “the people’s art project” will be only be available for a limited time and in limited editions, and no additional editions will ever be created or made available to the public. Initial projects for “the people’s art project” launched June 1, 2021.
